Services

Discover the range of services we offer to enhance your property management experience

Repairs & Maintenance

Our round-the-clock access to affordable and certified tradespeople means you get quality repairs and maintenance without any additional charges.

Property Inspections

We provide detailed inspection reports every three months, addressing maintenance concerns and ensuring your property's integrity.

Rent Collection

Our strict policy ensures timely rent collection, sparing you from any payment delays.

Property Knowledge

Our experienced property managers are well-versed in property regulations, ensuring legal compliance and peace of mind.

Property Marketing

We implement effective marketing strategies and thorough property viewings to attract high-quality tenants.

Tenancy Tribunal Representation

Our knowledgeable staff will represent you at the Tenancy Tribunal, safeguarding your rights throughout the process.

Methamphetamine Testing

We take proactive measures to protect your investment, minimizing the risk of drug contamination.

End of Year Financial Assistance

For end-of-year financials, we diligently back up all data, ensuring its safety and security.

Tenant Screening

Prior to accepting tenants, we conduct comprehensive credit and background checks, ensuring their financial stability and trustworthiness.

About us

At Rental Doctors, we are committed to redefining property management in Auckland. With a deep understanding of the local market, we offer tailored solutions that simplify and enhance your residential investment experience. Our experienced team combines industry expertise with a personal touch, ensuring your property receives the attention it deserves. We pride ourselves on going above and beyond to make your investment journey enjoyable and stress-free. Discover the Rental Doctors difference today.
